    <briefdescription>
<para>Shared memory layout for the ring buffer control structure. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Resides at the start of the shared memory region, followed by the slot data array. Each field group is cache-line-aligned to prevent false sharing between the writer and readers.</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">Shared<sp/>Memory<sp/>Layout:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">┌────────────────────────────────────────┐<sp/><sp/>offset<sp/>0</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>RingBufferHeader<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>┌──────────────────────────────────┐<sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>│<sp/>config<sp/>(immutable<sp/>after<sp/>init)<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/><ref refid="structconduit_1_1internal_1_1RingBufferHeader_1a0a799ca4cab2975d94c914198eac20a5" kindref="member">slot_count</ref>,<sp/><ref refid="structconduit_1_1internal_1_1RingBufferHeader_1a0b023e4492dc5c1788c1c04b9c9d3709" kindref="member">slot_size</ref>,<sp/>etc.<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>├──────────────────────────────────┤<sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/>aligned<sp/>64B</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>│<sp/><ref refid="structconduit_1_1internal_1_1RingBufferHeader_1a38294cb4f2556dbe58e613d3449f71be" kindref="member">write_idx</ref><sp/>(writer<sp/>only)<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>├──────────────────────────────────┤<sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/>aligned<sp/>64B</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>│<sp/><ref refid="structconduit_1_1internal_1_1RingBufferHeader_1ab9ec222a04c424e4259830c1596e37ed" kindref="member">subscriber_mask</ref><sp/>+<sp/><ref refid="structconduit_1_1internal_1_1RingBufferHeader_1a44ccf4d1d4718e0574aeed1f66eaf4da" kindref="member">futex_word</ref><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>├──────────────────────────────────┤<sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/>aligned<sp/>64B</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>│<sp/><ref refid="structconduit_1_1internal_1_1RingBufferHeader_1aff671b5815d43a320beefcf10ba7988e" kindref="member">read_idx</ref>[0..MAX_SUBSCRIBERS-1]<sp/><sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/>each<sp/>aligned<sp/>64B</highlight></codeline>
